OL,3,CTherme Manchester and the green
OL,4,Cwellness revolution
OL,6,FThe Austrian company behind the
OL,7,Fworld's biggest "wellbeing resort"
OL,8,Fsays its helping cities reconnect with
OL,9,Fnature and improving people's health.
OL,11,FTherme say their warm water lagoons
OL,12,Fare built to the highest green
OL,13,Fstandards, while they recycle millions
OL,14,Fof gallons of water and use natural
OL,15,Fgases to keep their spa pools clean.
OL,17,FManchester is joining Bucharest and
OL,18,Fcities around the world from Toronto,
OL,19,FWashington and Dubai embracing the
OL,20,Fhealth and wellness revolution.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
