OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778760670
OL,3,CTherme Manchester and the green
OL,4,Cwellness revolution
OL,6,FBut what will this huge demand for
OL,7,Fwater mean for people's bills?
OL,9,FTherma Manchester promises to bring
OL,10,Fthe beach to the city, and will be
OL,11,Fhome to more than 1500 palm trees and
OL,12,F800 thousand tropical plants.
OL,14,FThe sites will be powered by renewable
OL,15,Fenergy to reduce greenhouse gases to
OL,16,Fcombat climate change.
OL,18,FThe thermal pools in Bucharest are the
OL,19,Fblue print for Manchester which will
OL,20,Fbe the world's biggest wellness resort.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
