OL,3,CTherme Manchester and the green
OL,4,Cwellness revolution
OL,6,FThe resort's technical director gives
OL,7,Fspecialist tours underneath the spa
OL,8,Fpools to show how they meet the
OL,9,Fhighest green credentials
OL,11,FNicolaie Corbeanu said: "You can see
OL,12,Fthat all the palm tree, each one has a
OL,13,Fhumidity and temperature sensor."
OL,15,FEvery palm tree has an address and we
OL,16,Fknow how many litres of water with
OL,17,Fnutrients, the palm trees receive.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
