OL,3,CTherme Manchester and the green
OL,4,Cwellness revolution
OL,6,FTherme spa resorts use ozone gas and
OL,7,Fspecial filters to clean the entire
OL,8,Fquantity of their pools in just four
OL,9,Fhours, using minimum chlorine in the
OL,10,Fwater to meet regulations.
OL,12,FNicolaie said: "You can see the
OL,13,Fbubbles. All the bubbles are ozone
OL,14,Fgas, 99.9%.
OL,16,FIt's the most powerful process for
OL,17,Fcleaning and disinfection."
OL,19,F"Asked if he would drink it? "From the
OL,20,Fpool directly I can, drink the water
OL,21,Fthere, 100%."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
