OL,3,CTherme Manchester and the green
OL,4,Cwellness revolution
OL,6,FTherme Manchester will be a year round
OL,7,Fresort at a constant tropical 33
OL,8,Fdegrees, using solar energy, heat
OL,9,Fstorage, and millions of gallons of
OL,10,Fwater - but at what cost, particularly
OL,11,Fif there is a dry spell and water bans
OL,12,Fare mooted.
OL,14,FProfessor David Russel, Chief
OL,15,FExecutive of Therme Manchester said:
OL,16,F"We are lucky that a lot of rain falls
OL,17,Fin the Lake District
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
