OL,3,CTherme Manchester and the green
OL,4,Cwellness revolution
OL,6,F"92% of all the water we use in our
OL,7,Fpools, we have 35,000m of poles, or
OL,8,F92% of that is reused water everything
OL,9,Fwe're doing is with the climate and
OL,10,Fthe ecology elements of life
OL,11,Fconsidered.
OL,13,F:It certainly won't have an impact on
OL,14,Fbills. In fact have done anything. It
OL,15,Fshould make bills more economic.
OL,17,FIrina Wade is from Bucharest and is a
OL,18,Ffan of Therme and using saunas, which
OL,19,Fshe usually does three times a week.
OL,26,@oD@WOY
