OL,3,CTherme Manchester and the green
OL,4,Cwellness revolution
OL,6,FIrina said: c"I am even considering
OL,7,Fbuying a house close by so I can
OL,8,Factually go in and be there in
OL,9,FManchester. In Manchester? Exactly.
OL,10,FAnd I know that the house prices are
OL,11,Fnot really cheap in Manchester either,
OL,12,Fbut yeah, I'm really excited. So I
OL,13,Fwill be their biggest fan."
OL,15,FShe's not the only one, King Charles
OL,16,Fhas taken a keen interest in Therme
OL,17,Fand they've invited him to the opening
OL,18,Fin Manchester and asked the monarch to
OL,19,Fbe the first on the slide.
